Installation:

Installation of "WPBangla Login Master Plugin" is very easy. If you dont know how to install wordpress plugin, please follow the bellows instruction to install "WPbangla Login Master",

a. Download the ZIP package.
b. Open WordPress admin and go to Plugins -> Add New -> Upload. Browse for the ZIP file wpb-login-master.zip on your computer and hit “Install Now”.
c. Activate the plugin.

Requirements:

* WordPress v3.5 or greater
